# Web-safe video allowlist for files that actually ship with the site.
# Existing tracked files remain tracked, but new raw videos in public/videos/
# will stay ignored unless they use one of these safe naming patterns.
!public/videos/
!public/videos/**/
public/videos/**/*.mp4
public/videos/**/*.MP4
public/videos/**/*.mov
public/videos/**/*.MOV
!public/videos/**/*-h264.mp4
!public/videos/**/*-web.mp4
!public/videos/**/*-compressed.mp4

# Raw staging media
portfolio_media_staging/

# Local-only notes
LOCAL_VIDEO_COMPRESSION_README.md
